Package org.springframework.data.gemfire.config.admin

Class AbstractGemfireAdminOperations

java.lang.Object
org.springframework.data.gemfire.config.admin.AbstractGemfireAdminOperations
All Implemented Interfaces:
GemfireAdminOperations
Direct Known Subclasses:
FunctionGemfireAdminTemplate
public class AbstractGemfireAdminOperations extends Object implements GemfireAdminOperations
AbstractGemfireAdminOperations is an abstract base class encapsulating common functionality supporting administrative (management) operations against a Pivotal GemFire or Apache Geode cluster.
Since:
2.0.0
